sep.gaia.resources.wikipedia

Class WikipediaData

  • java.lang.Object
    • sep.gaia.resources.DataResource
      • sep.gaia.resources.poi.PointOfInterest
        • sep.gaia.resources.wikipedia.WikipediaData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class WikipediaData
extends PointOfInterest
    Concrete class WikipediaData inherits from DataResource. It contains everything that is necessary to create a wikipedia short description dialog. A WikipediaData dummy contains only the title of the related PointOfInterest. The specific wikipedia short description can be set by the Loader class. The valid flag inheritated by the parent DataResource class indicates, whether the WikipediaData contains the short description. The wikipedia information is taken of mediawiki.org api.
    Author:
    Michael Mitterer
